Scatter Charts
Group and set the scale to help users make sense of the data you are displaying.

Setting	DESCRIPTION
Plot By	Choose the grouping to display on your chart.
X Axis	Choose the values to display on the horizontal axis.
Y Axis	Choose what values to display on the vertical axis.
Group By	Choose how to group information on your chart.
Display Units	Change the measure for values displayed on the Y-axis of the chart.
Drill Down	Select where users go when they click the chart.
